{"tid":1884061,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"依架講緊係五千枝滅菌噴霧！！！！","createTime":"2020-02-17T11:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T15:47:14.000Z","uid":146909,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06240b2b802b3aec97f9e843ead1d0ac9be3944f","tid":1884061,"uid":146909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"大家好! 我地係一班乖孫<br />\n首先, 希望睇到呢個post嘅人都身體健康 (黑警, 藍絲, 五毛除外)<br />\n好, 正題係, 乖孫見到肺炎disco橫行, 啲消毒物資比人搶到七七八八, 價錢漲到炒黃牛咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口罩我地就冇嘞, 但係就咁啱有啲滅菌噴霧, 依家平過市價一半放出嚟, 希望幫到大家。<br />\n我地買入左五千枝，希望大家一齊散出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同其他酒精搓手液唔同既係可以放心用於嬰兒同寵物用品！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1bwMEK8dC4SRuHW-TfaPK4tvYtUhE3b5LA2OsrYHlfEw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1bwMEK8dC4SRuHW-TfaPK4tvYtUhE3b5LA2OsrYHlfEw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b728fbab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1bwMEK8dC4SRuHW-TfaPK4tvYtUhE3b5LA2OsrYHlfEw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n平時出街食飯，餐具未必乾淨！<br />\n特別而家肺炎情況咁嚴重👍🏻👍🏻<br />\n食嘢之前可以幫餐具消一消毒<br />\n可以直接噴於面部及身體皮膚<br />\n傷口消毒<br />\n噴於蔬菜滅菌免沖洗<br />\n任何日常用品<br />\n空氣淨化<br />\n無懼接觸眼耳口費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PBT2o9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBT2o9k.png&h=b27d558c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQZ1EHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQZ1EHK.jpg&h=c589372e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLGvx2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLGvx2L.jpg&h=28008db7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2L7q6nM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2L7q6nM.jpg&h=24f8315c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLtefhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLtefhc.jpg&h=cea96c81&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyuH8Cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyuH8Cd.jpg&h=64754a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後,<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n好人一世平安，香港人要自救<br />\n希望可以幫到大家，同大家一齊渡過難關"},{"pid":"b4b7f1b6faf992eb7e663e5a3a51c70638f4e2da","tid":1884061,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"滅菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁病毒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826c662ccdd7ab1f741311914c1ca75b23197f40","tid":1884061,"uid":4108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdc56816d35b9a69046d35955150011e211babb","tid":1884061,"uid":146909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4b7f1b6faf992eb7e663e5a3a51c70638f4e2da","tid":1884061,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"滅菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁病毒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0